text: Ashraf Uddin Khan Imu is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Dhaka-12. ==Career== Imu was elected to parliament from Dhaka-12 in 1988 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate. He is the Vice- President of Dhaka District unit of Bangladesh Awami League. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Ashraf Uddin Khan Imu
